{"tid":966791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果以中國需求下降為由下調收入預期","createTime":"2019-01-03T05:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T00:28:30.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb2dffd07f2e50f74e439ff29f906ea62d68942","tid":966791,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"蘋果以中國需求下降為由下調收入預期<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001080927?full=y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001080927%3Ffull%3Dy&d=9M7Xd7PTM5cbQZimQZnUp4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c7fc873f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001080927?full=y</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果(Apple)在周三晚些時候極其罕見地發布了一份收入警告，將收入預期比之前預期下調10%歸咎於中國經濟疲弱以及發達國家蘋果iPhone更新換代情況令人失望。此舉令華爾街感到震驚。<br />\n<br />\n這一消息使蘋果的股票在盤後交易中下跌逾7%，並引發了投資者對全球經濟前景的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果首席執行官蒂姆&bull;庫克(Tim Cook)在給投資者的公開信中試圖儘可能淡化收入預期下調的程度。他在信中寫道，蘋果曾預測，與上一年這一財季的883億美元相比，本財年將只能實現「收入略微增長」。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果表示，幾乎所有令人失望的結果都可以歸咎於中國經濟放緩。蘋果還表示，其收入下降「超過百分之百」可以歸咎於中國對iPhone、Mac電腦和iPad的需求降低。<br />\n<br />\n庫克表示：「儘管我們預測到關鍵新興市場會出現一些挑戰，我們沒有預測到經濟減速的程度，尤其是在大中華區。」他還聲稱，日益加劇的貿易緊張影響了經濟環境。<br />\n<br />\n然而，蘋果也指出，發達國家對iPhone的需求弱於預期，更新換代成新款iPhone手機的用戶比預期中要少。蘋果將這歸咎於經濟疲弱、移動運營商提供的補貼減少，以及蘋果最近推出的電池更換補貼，這項服務使更多人選擇繼續使用現有的手機。"},{"pid":"b4f56204831518a525465ba88b92026a664f27ac","tid":966791,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"美爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c370350ca8c23da7d65e46be3bcf8b2f8af54c28","tid":966791,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:22:03.000Z","msg":"華為又贏"},{"pid":"ddab5231d5969e1d40fa3a2e19a5d1c2d1adc6f7","tid":966791,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T00:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb269353754932026c99bf361be7769aa4aa58fc","tid":966791,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T00:05:20.000Z","msg":"認清事實啦好心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa59bc06cff0d6a3ab135cf0785cf6e94f7b5bb","tid":966791,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T00:05:30.000Z","msg":"驚閪<br />\n下一部iPhone Xi 賣到兩萬蚊一部<br />\n肯定賺返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeff30ef5a773e2a1cd18a70c7e00a998c68a081","tid":966791,"uid":34550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T00:19:49.000Z","msg":"直接下部ip 10k 起跳，填番條數。無錢唔肯分期G持既沒資格做果粉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34809a0b96e56f57fdf39fbec352657c1dc090d6","tid":966791,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5fa59bc06cff0d6a3ab135cf0785cf6e94f7b5bb","tid":966791,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T00:05:30.000Z","msg":"驚閪<br />\n下一部iPhone Xi 賣到兩萬蚊一部<br />\n肯定賺返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T00:21:24.000Z","msg":"全部機紅色<br />\n蘋果logo轉党logo<br />\n開機畫面預設president Xi<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肯定大賣"},{"pid":"8bf66a259801857e82db8548e55956afed2b4e22","tid":966791,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T00:28:30.000Z","msg":"賣咁貴 換你老母"}]}